@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<style>
    .about-us {
        background-color: #E6D4B8;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .about-us h1 {
        font-size: 2.5em;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .about-us p {
        font-size: 1.2em;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .about-us .values {
        margin-top: 40px;
    }
    .about-us .value-item {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .about-us .value-item h3 {
        font-size: 1.5em;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .about-us .value-item p {
        font-size: 1.1em;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }
</style>

<div class="container about-us">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p>Welcome to KhumaloCraft! We are a company dedicated to providing the highest quality products to our customers. Our mission is to blend craftsmanship with innovation, creating unique and desirable products that enhance the lives of our customers.</p>
    <p>Founded in [Year], KhumaloCraft has grown from a small startup to a reputable brand known for its commitment to quality and customer satisfaction. We believe in the power of creativity and the importance of staying true to our values.</p>

    <div class="values">
        <h2>Our Values</h2>

        <div class="value-item">
            <h3>Quality</h3>
            <p>We prioritize quality in everything we do. From the materials we use to the craftsmanship of our products, we strive for excellence.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-item">
            <h3>Innovation</h3>
            <p>Innovation drives us forward. We embrace new technologies and ideas to continuously improve and stay ahead in the industry.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-item">
            <h3>Customer Satisfaction</h3>
            <p>Our customers are at the heart of our business. We are committed to providing exceptional service and products that meet their needs.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

